g.text: In the following we assume initial raw sequence data pass basic validation
We also treat each sequence separately (for each sequence a separate path is possible)
Validation errors should be loudly logged and brought to the attention of the admin
log validation errors so that they can be reviewed by admin
Store processed sequence data with errors
Store processed sequence data without errors
respond with processed sequence data (if available) and warnings/errors
respond with processed sequence data (if available) and warnings/errors
email reminder to user to approve/reject processed sequence data
